show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/EXZYXph1mCajxK6P7
show.description: "The Female Lead is the Strongest Mouthpiece Substitute" is a short Chinese drama series that centers on a sharp-witted woman who steps into someone else's identity—becoming a powerful and fearless substitute in a world filled with manipulation, politics, and hidden agendas. Though originally underestimated, she proves to be a formidable force, using her intelligence and boldness to challenge corrupt authority and protect those she cares about. With a blend of intrigue, romance, and empowerment, the series follows her journey as she navigates dangerous court dynamics, uncovers secrets, and rises to become the strongest voice in a place where silence was once expected.
